Warining: This branch is still under development

This README file contains information on the contents of the
ad-datacard layer.

Please see the corresponding sections below for details.


Dependencies
============

This layer depends on:

  URI: git://git.yoctoproject.org/poky
  branch: thud

  URI: git://git.openembedded.org/openembedded-core
  layers: meta
  branch: thud

  URI: https://github.com/Xilinx/meta-xilinx.git
  layers: meta-xilinx-bsp
  branch: thud

  URI: https://github.com/adps/meta-admxrc9r1
  branch: thud



Patches
=======

Please submit any patches against the ad-datacard layer to
maintainer:

Maintainer: Christopher Holyoake <ch@alpha-data.com>


